{"data":[{"date":"09:14 25/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ajax vs Sturm Graz 01h30 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-ajax-vs-sturm-graz-01h30-ngay-267-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ajax vs Sturm Graz l\u00fac 01h30 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ajax vs Sturm Graz 01h30 ng\u00e0y 267 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ajax vs Sturm Graz 01h30 ng\u00e0y 267 Champions League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Ajax-vs-Sturm-Graz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ajax vs Sturm Graz</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Ajax vs Sturm Graz: 0-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, b\u1ec1 d\u00e0y th\u00e0nh t\u00edch, v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, Sturm Graz t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean thua xa so v\u1edbi Ajax. Ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang con s\u1ed1 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111o\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap C1/Champions League l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u00c1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1eady n\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Ajax trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai. Song, xem x\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch nh\u1ea5t H\u00e0 lan ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, vi\u1ec7c Ajax \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o \u00e1nh h\u00e0o quang qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, ch\u1ee9 v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e3 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp Ajax \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Ajax c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 quan. Tr\u1ea3i qua 7 m\u00e0n th\u1eed l\u1eeda, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 tr\u1eadn, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 2, thua 4, m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Walsall, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng 3 Anh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, Sturm Graz v\u1eeba m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 t\u1ea1i C\u00fap QG \u00c1o. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 6/7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1614","checkdouble":"191970"},{"date":"10:28 25/07","title":"Anthony Martial ti\u1ebfn b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn...Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/anthony-martial-tien-buoc-dai-denchelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Anthony Martial t\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Mourinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Anthony Martial \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Mourinho, Anthony Martial t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi Mourinho, Anthony Martial t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/Khong-hai-long-voi-Mourinho,-Anthony-Martial-toi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 23, \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Martial l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Martial\u201d.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, song HLV\u00a0 Jose Mourinho l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Martial r\u1eddi Old Trafford m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 v\u1edbi San Jose c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTrong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1i g\u00ec mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt, song M.U l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 6\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3, v\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n trong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Martial quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Anthony Martial t\u1edbi Chelsea l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial se dut ao chia tay MU he nay\" title=\"Martial s\u1ebd d\u1ee9t \u00e1o chia tay MU h\u00e8 n\u00e0y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-247,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eddi M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Mourinho khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Theo The Sun, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n\u00a0s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-martial-co-the-cap-ben-tottenham-vao-tuan-toi-172-187859.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Martial</span>, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. The Blues d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi \u0111\u1ee7 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda M.U y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ef1u sao Monaco, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm Martial nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Eden Hazard.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Martial v\u1edbi M.U ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 12 th\u00e1ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Old Trafford, n\u1ebfu M.U kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n anh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1613","checkdouble":"191971"},{"date":"09:32 25/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Celtic vs Rosenborg 01h45 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-celtic-vs-rosenborg-01h45-ngay-267-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U m\u1ea5t t\u1edbi 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mat-7-cau-thu-quan-trong-mu-se-da-the-nao-o-vong-mo-man-nha-mua-toi-172-191532.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U s\u1ebd v\u1eafng t\u1edbi 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA 2018/19</span> g\u1eb7p Leicester. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Paul Pogba, Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashford, Jesse Lingard, Marouane Fellaini, Ashley Young v\u00e0 Phil Jones s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-MU-truoc-viec-mat-7-cau-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U v\u1eafng 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 55 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh n\u0103m nay b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 10/08.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng MU b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho rat muon tai hop voi Willian o MU\" title=\"Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Willian \u1edf MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a M.U b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Arsenal v\u00e0 Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cChelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. M.U, Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi v\u1eafng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i nh\u00ecn sang Leicester, n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng sai, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Jamie Vardy v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o Brighton, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng v\u1eafng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0o v\u00ec World Cup. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t sung s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u00e2y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester v\u00e0 Brighton v\u1edbi M.U kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1612","checkdouble":"191972"},{"date":"10:29 25/07","title":"Everton ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Premier League 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/everton-kich-no-bom-tan-premier-league-50-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRicharlison t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p th\u1ea7y c\u0169<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Everton \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Marco Silva \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 Mourinho \u0111\u1ec7 nh\u1ecb. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, khi l\u00f4i k\u00e9o c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 Richarlison t\u1eeb CLB Watford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Silva \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Richarlison v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 11,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u1eeb CLB Brazil Fluminense. Ch\u1ec9 1 n\u0103m sau, \u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. M\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 5 n\u0103m c\u00f9ng l\u1eddi h\u1ecfi mua 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed1t, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed khi\u1ebfn Everton ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p th\u1ea7y c\u0169, bom t\u1ea5n Richarlison cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Everton. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Marco Silva. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/everton-kich-no-bom-tan-premier-league-50-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea1i Watford, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi nhau. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 d\u1ea1y t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Brazil. Marco Silva c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap t\u00f4i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cEverton \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u00f4i v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n vinh danh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a CLB v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. T\u00f4i \u0111ang kh\u00e1t khao thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1p l\u1ea1i l\u1eddi tri \u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, HLV Marco Silva c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap CLB c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Brazil r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed sau l\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Richarlison v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 r\u1ebb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/21/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\">\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</span><br>\r\nEverton mu\u1ed1n mua Lucas Digne c\u1ee7a Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh dung c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham-172-191673.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-muon-roi-crystal-palace-va-tin-vui-cho-tottenham-172-191673.html\">Sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh NHA b\u00e1o tin vui cho Tottenham</span><br>\r\nZaha mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Crystal Palace v\u00e0 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tin vui cho m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t CLB \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Everton, Tottenham hay Borussia...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1611","checkdouble":"191974"},{"date":"10:58 25/07","title":"T\u1edbi Juve, Emre Can tri \u00e2n th\u1ea7y c\u0169","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/16/toi-juve-emre-can-tri-an-thay-cu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n sang Serie A t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do, Emre Can tri \u00e2n HLV Klopp khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Klopp<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 4 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u01a1i cho Juventus mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. \u0110\u1ec3 n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ra \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p, Emre Can \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n HLV \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Jurgen Klopp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u1edbi Klopp lu\u00f4n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00fac t\u00f4i may m\u1eafn khi t\u00f4i th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1eddi Liverpool trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n Emre Can c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i. Nh\u01b0ng &ldquo;b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i&rdquo;, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Cris Ronaldo. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Ronaldo. B\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5y, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juve, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can tri \u00e2n HLV Klopp\" title=\"Emre Can gia nh\u1eadp Juventus b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/chinh-thuc-emre-can-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juve, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can tri \u00e2n HLV Klopp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i xem nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f9ng chung chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, d\u00f9 c\u00e1c CLB Italia kh\u00e1c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2u. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Turin, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0o d\u1ef1 \u00e1n l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a CLB.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A, v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Champions League. Juve \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, v\u00e0 n\u0103m nay c\u0169ng \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Liverpool, Emre Can tri \u00e2n HLV Klopp nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Fabinho &ndash; Keita.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua-172-191977.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua-172-191977.html\">Mourinho: Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n MU \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a</span><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/khong-du-dau-cung-juventus-cristiano-ronaldo-sang-trung-quoc-quang-ba-thuong-hieu-176-191950.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/6.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/khong-du-dau-cung-juventus-cristiano-ronaldo-sang-trung-quoc-quang-ba-thuong-hieu-176-191950.html\">Kh\u00f4ng du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Juventus, Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u00f9ng Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 Nike c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n mang t\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1610","checkdouble":"191975"},{"date":"10:53 25/07","title":"Mourinho: \"Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u01a1n MU \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U m\u1ea5t t\u1edbi 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mat-7-cau-thu-quan-trong-mu-se-da-the-nao-o-vong-mo-man-nha-mua-toi-172-191532.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U s\u1ebd v\u1eafng t\u1edbi 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA 2018/19</span> g\u1eb7p Leicester. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Paul Pogba, Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashford, Jesse Lingard, Marouane Fellaini, Ashley Young v\u00e0 Phil Jones s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c m\u1ea5t 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-MU-truoc-viec-mat-7-cau-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn M.U v\u1eafng 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 55 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh n\u0103m nay b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 10/08.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng MU b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho rat muon tai hop voi Willian o MU\" title=\"Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Willian \u1edf MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/mourinho-chelsea-liverpool-va-arsenal-co-loi-the-hon-mu-o-giai-doan-dau-mua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a M.U b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Chelsea, Arsenal v\u00e0 Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cChelsea, Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. M.U, Man City v\u00e0 Tottenham g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi v\u1eafng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i nh\u00ecn sang Leicester, n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng sai, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Jamie Vardy v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o Brighton, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng v\u1eafng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0o v\u00ec World Cup. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t sung s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u00e2y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester v\u00e0 Brighton v\u1edbi M.U kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1609","checkdouble":"191977"},{"date":"11:20 25/07","title":"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng: Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 38 tu\u1ed5i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/cuc-nong-chelsea-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-38-tuoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robert Green, The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, theo \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 38 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Robert Green</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo The Sun, Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robert Green. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 38 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robert Green h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robert Green h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/cuc-nong-chelsea-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-38-tuoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Robert Green</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00e1ng 8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Green k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Huddersfield, song d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi David Wagner anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 38 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Huddersfield \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2018, anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1i. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian t\u00ednh to\u00e1n anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London the d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Chelsea kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Robert Green.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 38 tu\u1ed5i, Chelsea s\u1ebd t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Pepe Reina. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Robert Green cho th\u1ea5y The Blues s\u1eafp chia tay Thibaut Courtois ho\u1eb7c Willy Caballero.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGreen \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 658 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong 19 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 12 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh. Theo Mirror, Robert Green \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 thay Caballero, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00e2n binh Robert Green v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f2n l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. HLV Sarri x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Chelsea \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"sarri\" title=\"sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/Chu-tich-Napoli-chi-trich-HLV-Sarri-phu-bac-voi-doi-bong-cu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cK\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kho\u1ea3ng 2 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa m\u1edbi kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, Chelsea quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 151 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua b\u1ed9 ba Higuain, Rugani v\u00e0 Pjanic c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-morata-neu-roi-chelsea-172-191433.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Morata cho AC Milan</span>, David Luiz v\u00e0 Gary Cahill c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1608","checkdouble":"191978"},{"date":"11:17 25/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 25/7: M.U \"t\u1ed5ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng\" Willian","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/ngay-hom-nay-257.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (25/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2>(lien t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>M.U \"t\u1ed5ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng\" Willian\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 257, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 257, tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-257,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\nC\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Chelsea ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 Mourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1ea5t. Willian t\u1eebng c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng Mourinho, n\u00ean gi\u1eef m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 kh\u00e1 m\u1eadt thi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian qua, Barca quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Willian, ba l\u1ea7n tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ti\u1ec1n cao nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea v\u1eabn l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. R\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed r\u1ebb h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Malcom c\u1ee7a Bordeaux (t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 45,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd Malcom, Barca r\u00fat lui trong v\u1ee5 Willian, m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho MU nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o l\u00f4i k\u00e9o tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. Hi\u1ec7n Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t s\u1ed1t ru\u1ed9t v\u00ec s\u1ef1 tr\u1ea7m l\u1eafng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, \u00f4ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y s\u1ebfp l\u1edbn MU ra tay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Willian cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu ph\u00eda MU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Willian, l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb nghi\u00eam t\u00fac.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chap-nhan-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-willian-172-191968.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/mu-chap-nhan-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-willian.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chap-nhan-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-willian-172-191968.html\">MU th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Willian</span><br>\r\n<span>MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Willian, theo Mundo Deportivo Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Everton \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Richarlison</h2>\r\nX\u00e1c nh\u1eadn tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7, Everton cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Richarlison t\u1eeb Watford v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n H\u0110 5 n\u0103m. Theo SkySport, The Toffees \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb 21 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-kich-no-bom-tan-premier-league-50-trieu-bang-172-191974.html\">Everton ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n Premier League 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1eadt k\u00e8o v\u1edbi Roma, Malcom t\u1edbi Barca</h2>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia nh\u1eadp Olympico v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Roma x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00f3t, Malcom l\u1ea1i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barcelona. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam qua. Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Brazil \u0111\u00e3 k\u00ed H\u0110 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed kho\u1ea3ng 41 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barcelona c\u01b0\u1edbp th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i AS Roma</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u00f9 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c sau AS Roma nh\u01b0ng Barcelona l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom khi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi h\u01a1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea theo s\u00e1t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thiago</h2>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chia tay Thiago Alcantara. T\u1edd ESPN kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, MU c\u00f3 quan t\u00e2m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ec7n ch\u00ed, trong khi Chelsea kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i. Tuy nhi\u00ean Barca m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i v\u1eadt l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t.\r\n<h2>Sao 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Bakayoko \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri r\u1eb1ng anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Stamford Bridge. T\u1edd Estadio Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1edbi Bakayoko. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf Steven N\u2019Zonzi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bakayoko-gap-mat-sarri-doi-ra-di-172-191938.html\">Bakayoko g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t Sarri \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Sevilla l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 Arsenal</h2>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Steven N'Zonzi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo Marca, Sevilla tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu \"Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7\" ch\u1ecbu chi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng (30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).\r\n<h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Modric</h2>\r\nTottenham \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, ph\u00eda Real Madrid ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia r\u1eddi Bernabeu. Modric 33 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u1ef1c k\u00ec d\u1ebbo dai. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, anh \u0111\u01b0a Croatia v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft (ch\u1ec9 thua Ph\u00e1p).\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 257 MU t\u1ed5ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Willian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 257 MU t\u1ed5ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Willian h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-257-MU-tong-tan-cong-Willian-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>James kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Bayern</h2>\r\n\u201cHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. CLB cho th\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Real Madrid, d\u00f9 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho l\u1eafm. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 36 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f9ng 42 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n khi l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 CLB t\u00f4i g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t\".<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1607","checkdouble":"191979"},{"date":"11:22 25/07","title":"G\u00f3c Liverpool: Qua r\u1ed3i th\u1eddi d\u00f9ng dao \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c x\u1ea1 th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/goc-liverpool-qua-roi-thoi-dung-dao-dau-voi-cac-xa-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d m\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 cho nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mua s\u1eafm kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mo Salah t\u1eeb AS Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36,7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a CLB v\u00f9ng Merseyside trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec ph\u1ebf tru\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng &ldquo;bom x\u1ecbt&rdquo; Andy Carroll (gia nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 36,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i). H\u01a1n 1 n\u0103m sau, c\u00f3 ai ng\u1edd <u>Salah t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 5 trong danh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool</u> cao gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool Qua r\u1ed3i th\u1eddi d\u00f9ng dao \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c x\u1ea1 th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool Qua r\u1ed3i th\u1eddi d\u00f9ng dao \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c x\u1ea1 th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/11/Chuyen-nhuong-Liverpool-Qua-roi-thoi-dung-dao-dau-voi-cac-xa-thu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Naby Keita (53,4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), Fabinho (40 tri\u1ec7u), Xherdan Shaqiri (13,1 tri\u1ec7u) v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Alisson (55,7) n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Anfield. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, n\u1ebfu Liverpool kh\u00f4ng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Nabil Fekir, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 th\u00eam &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; c\u00f2n Salah xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 6.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua, <strong>suy ngh\u0129 v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i</strong>. M\u1ed9t Salah tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 v\u1edbi 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u1edd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/Robbie-Fowler-phat-bieu-ve-Alisson-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Alisson g\u1ea7n g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i Salah</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u1edbn c\u0169ng \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n</em>. M\u1ed9t v\u00e0i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u00ecn nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o HLV Jurgen Klopp v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. C\u00f2n gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, \u00e1nh m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ed3n v\u00e0o c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i kim ti\u1ec1n, gi\u00e1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u0103ng l\u00ean phi m\u00e3. G\u1ea7n 2 th\u00e1ng sau khi Liverpool ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng CLB v\u1edbi Salah, PSG ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i: 197 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mang v\u1ec1 Neymar t\u1eeb Barcelona. Th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson: Khi &ldquo;bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t&rdquo; t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\n<span>Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho AS Roma. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp theo \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean cao h\u01a1n. L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <em>th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng d\u00f9 l\u1edbn hay nh\u1ecf, m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 thu\u1eadn</em>. The Kop ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e2u ra ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00e2y t\u00f2 m\u00f2 v\u00e0 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1eb1ng <strong>th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n</strong>. V\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Virgil van Dijk, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u00e0 \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. V\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ph\u00e1 s\u00e2u k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Alisson, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1edbn h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson Fabinho Keita\" title=\"Alisson Fabinho Keita\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Alisson-Fabinho-Keita.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng &quot;bom t\u1ea5n&quot; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 th\u00edch nghi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh Liverpool l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 Klopp, ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft khai th\u00e1c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Roberto Firmino l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brendan Rodgers \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFirmino c\u00f9ng Salah v\u00e0 Sadio Mane ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng <em>t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng</em> h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Keita, Fabinho hay Alisson. B\u1ed9 ba MFS c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Shaqiri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i Premier League c\u00f9ng Stoke v\u00e0 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng Th\u1ee5y S\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge can thiet cho Liverpool\" title=\"Sturridge can thiet cho Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Sturridge-can-thiet-cho-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League</strong> thay v\u00ec nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 gi\u1eefa m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Rafa Benitez, C\u0110V c\u1ee7a The Kop m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0 Man City, Man United, Chelsea hay Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Van Dijk, Fabinho, Alisson hay Shaqiri trong 1 n\u0103m qua. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh sau 28 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp tu tin gianh danh hieu cung Liverpool\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/klopp-nam-nay-se-la-nam-cua-chung-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c chinh ph\u1ee5c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng 15 n\u0103m qua, Liverpool t\u1ecf ra l\u00e9p v\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U h\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Alex Ferguson r\u1ed3i Chelsea, Man City v\u1edbi t\u00fai ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1y. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, M.U \u0111\u00e3 suy y\u1ebfu th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Sir Alex trong khi Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, Man City m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y <u>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</u>. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mang dao \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c x\u1ea1 th\u1ee7. C\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-sturridge-o-lai-liverpool-la-dieu-tot-cho-tat-ca-172-191904.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-xay-ra-sau-khi-liverpool-chieu-mo-alisson-becker-172-191685.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau khi Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson Becker</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chieu-mo-thu-mon-alisson-dau-roi-loi-mia-mai-172-191662.html\">Liverpool bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-becker-giai-ma-tan-binh-liverpool-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191660.html\">Alisson Becker: Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 t\u00e2n binh Liverpool &ndash; th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chieu-mo-alisson-ho-da-co-de-gea-cua-rieng-minh-172-191659.html\">Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson: H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 De Gea c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1606","checkdouble":"191980"},{"date":"11:32 25/07","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 25/07","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/chuyen-nhuong-barca-hot-nhat-ngay-2507.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 25/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2507 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2507 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Chuyen-nhuong-Barca-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2507-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Malcom ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca 2018 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barcelona c\u01b0\u1edbp th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i AS Roma</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c sau AS Roma nh\u01b0ng Barcelona l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom khi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi h\u01a1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn quan t\u00e2m Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Barca ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin cho r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ousmane Dembele mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Malcom, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, hi\u1ec7n Chelsea \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Coutinho th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec Barca kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Coutinho se rat vui neu Willian toi Barca\" title=\"Coutinho s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui n\u1ebfu Willian t\u1edbi Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/coutinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Coutinho th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi Willian kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Willian, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30. Theo Sport, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Coutinho t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Willian \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Andre Gomes c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Tottenham v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Daily Mail, v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8 n\u00e0y Tottenham s\u1ebd cho ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n binh Andre Gomes t\u1eeb Barca, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 30 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Inter v\u00e0 Roma \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec Aleix Vidal</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, Inter Milan v\u00e0 Roma l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Aleix Vidal c\u1ee7a Barca, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Everton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mina quyet o lai Barca\" title=\"Mina quy\u1ebft \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/nguoi-hung-colombia-quyet-tam-bam-tru-tai-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Sport, Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8.\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Messi v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Marcos Alonso</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Sport, Messi v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Marcos Alonso c\u1ee7a Chelsea. M10 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Jasper Cillessen</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Theo Goal, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jasper Cillessen c\u1ee7a Barca trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Courtois t\u1edbi Real, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1605","checkdouble":"191981"},{"date":"07:01 25/07","title":"Kh\u00f4ng du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Juventus, Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/6.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u00f9ng Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 Nike c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n mang t\u00ean CR7.\r\n\r\n</h2><div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Cristiano-Ronaldo-sang-Trung-Quoc-quang-ba-thuong-hieu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Kh\u00f4ng du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Juventus do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018, Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gay chu y khi luon duoc mot ve si luc luong theo sat nhu hinh voi bong.\" title=\"Ronaldo g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd khi lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ec7 s\u0129 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng theo s\u00e1t nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd khi lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ec7 s\u0129 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng theo s\u00e1t nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo sang Trung Quoc de quang ba cho Nike cung nhu thuong hieu CR7 cua ban than. Nike coi Trung Quoc la thi truong trong diem, trong khi Adidas dat trong tam thi truong o Nhat Ban.\" title=\"Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho Nike c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u CR7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Nike coi Trung Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong khi Adidas \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/065845-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho Nike c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u CR7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Nike coi Trung Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong khi Adidas \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gop mat o Trung tam The thao Olympic Bac Kinh de day cac cau thu tre mot so ky nang co ban.\" title=\"Ronaldo g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf Trung t\u00e2m Th\u1ec3 thao Olympic B\u1eafc Kinh \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf Trung t\u00e2m Th\u1ec3 thao Olympic B\u1eafc Kinh \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cau thu 33 tuoi cung bieu dien ky thuat ca nhan de truyen cam hung cho cac cau thu tre.\" title=\"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen di cua Ronaldo toi Trung Quoc du kien se keo dai 1 tuan.\" title=\"Chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1edbi Trung Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 1 tu\u1ea7n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1edbi Trung Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 1 tu\u1ea7n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-vang-mat-trong-chuyen-du-dau-he-cua-juventus-176-191800.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-kiem-them-bao-nhieu-tien-cho-juventus-176-191796.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam kho\u1ea3ng bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/neymar-tin-ronaldo-se-toa-sang-tren-dat-y-176-191698.html\">Neymar tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/ronaldo-cap-ben-turin-juve-co-con-la-juve-389-191603.html\">Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Turin:  Juve c\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0\u2026 Juve?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-bi-in-mat-len-giay-ve-sinh-188-191598.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo b\u1ecb in m\u1eb7t l\u00ean ... gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ronaldo-ra-di-ai-se-mang-ve-50-ban-thang-moi-mua-cho-real-187-191545.html\">Ronaldo ra \u0111i: Ai s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a cho Real?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1604","checkdouble":"191950"},{"date":"07:46 25/07","title":"Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a FIFA: Mbappe s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Ronaldo, Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/danh-sach-cau-thu-hay-nhat-nam-cua-fifa-mbappe-sanh-vai-cung-ronaldo-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Leon Bailey r\u1eddi Bayer Leverkusen \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo The Sun, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-bundesliga-len-70-trieu-bang-172-187291.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Leon Bailey</span> c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/26/Leon-Bailey-roi-Bayer-Leverkusen-toi-Ngoai-hang-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997, HLV Emery nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica thay th\u1ebf Danny Welbeck, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Bailey l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Bayer Leverkusen, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Bundesliga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, n\u1ebfu t\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf Bundesliga anh c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Bailey s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, anh c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 trung phong c\u1eafm. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Arsenal ho\u1eb7c Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayer Leverkusen gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Leon Bailey</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey, Bayer Leverkusen \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/9/Hang-hot-Bundesliga-danh-tieng-voi-Chelsea-va-Arsenal-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayer Leverkusen \u0111\u00f2i 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho\u00a0</span>Leon Bailey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Sun, Bayer Leverkusen mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.\u00a0Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Leon Bailey ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Chelsea hay Arsenal m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1603","checkdouble":"191953"},{"date":"08:07 25/07","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/cong-phuong-chan-thuong-khong-the-tap-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin kh\u00f4ng vui khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham gia c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00e2n binh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n kheo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong chan thuong day chang khien HLV Park Hang Seo lo lang.\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo lo l\u1eafng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/cong-phuong-chan-thuong-khong-the-tap-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo lo l\u1eafng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea1y ch\u1eadm 1 v\u00f2ng s\u00e2n r\u1ed3i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, ch\u01b0\u1eddm \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e1. Theo c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng 2-3 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c. HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng d\u00f9 \u00f4ng g\u1ecdi 7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho c\u00fap t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi c\u00f3 17/30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n mu\u1ed9n v\u00ec b\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, SLNA v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean, c\u00f2n Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o PVF (H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean) cho \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 30/7. Sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu c\u00fap t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ba \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi l\u00e0 U23 Oman, U23 Palestine v\u00e0 U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau C\u00fap t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n sang Indonesia \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh khi m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i do s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 &quot;qu\u00ean&quot; UAE v\u00e0 Palestine c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-dang-van-lam-khong-nghi-toi-chuyen-thang-thua-khi-len-tuyen-168-191943.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m t\u1ea1o \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi th\u00f4ng minh khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-mang-luc-luong-rat-manh-sang-doi-dau-u23-viet-nam-tai-cup-tu-hung-168-191940.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Cup T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-khong-ngai-boc-tham-lai-asiad-168-191909.html\">Sao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/gia-ve-xem-u23-viet-nam-thi-dau-co-nguy-co-e-vi-qua-cao-168-191889.html\">Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 xem U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb \u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon-292-191799.html\">Nh\u1eefng ai trong \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nN.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1602","checkdouble":"191954"},{"date":"08:38 25/07","title":"\"Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal nh\u01b0ng Ramsey th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/welbeck-co-the-roi-arsenal-nhung-ramsey-thi-khong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ray Parlor ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Danny Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates c\u00f2n Aaron Ramsey th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong v\u00f2ng 12 th\u00e1ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 chia tay v\u1edbi 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, bao g\u1ed3m Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain, Theo Walcott v\u00e0 Jack Wilshere.\u00a0Danny Welbeck \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u1ee9 4 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ray Parlor ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ray Parlor ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Ray-Parlor-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb b\u00e1n \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. Nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Welbeck, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/voi-15-trieu-bang-welbeck-la-mon-hoi-voi-moi-doi-bong-172-191759.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal\u00a0b\u00e1n Welbeck</span> n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung \u1edf Premier League \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ef1u sao M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRay Parlor ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Danny Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. S\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Emirates \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129\u00a0Welbeck v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n cho Arsenal, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng sau Aubameyang, Lacazette, Ozil v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Emery kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n Welbeck, Arsenal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. R\u1eddi Emirates l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i v\u1edbi Welbeck, n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n Ramsey</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ray Parlor kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Welbeck nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Ramsey, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Welbeck co the roi Arsenal nhung Ramsey thi khong\" title=\"Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal nh\u01b0ng Ramsey th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/081447-ramsey.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal nh\u01b0ng Ramsey th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 Arsenal ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef Aaron Ramsey, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 sau khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Jack Wilshere ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Lucas Torreira\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRamsey c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Frank Lampard. Arsenal c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1601","checkdouble":"191955"},{"date":"08:55 25/07","title":"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/9/bailey-danh-tieng-voi-chelsea-va-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Leon Bailey r\u1eddi Bayer Leverkusen \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo The Sun, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-bundesliga-len-70-trieu-bang-172-187291.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Leon Bailey</span> c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/26/Leon-Bailey-roi-Bayer-Leverkusen-toi-Ngoai-hang-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997, HLV Emery nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica thay th\u1ebf Danny Welbeck, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Bailey l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Bayer Leverkusen, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Bundesliga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, n\u1ebfu t\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf Bundesliga anh c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Bailey s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, anh c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 trung phong c\u1eafm. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Arsenal ho\u1eb7c Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayer Leverkusen gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Leon Bailey</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey, Bayer Leverkusen \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/9/Hang-hot-Bundesliga-danh-tieng-voi-Chelsea-va-Arsenal-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayer Leverkusen \u0111\u00f2i 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho\u00a0</span>Leon Bailey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Sun, Bayer Leverkusen mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.\u00a0Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Leon Bailey ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Chelsea hay Arsenal m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1600","checkdouble":"191957"}]}